<i>noun</i>: 언급 [언급], 거명 [거ː명] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>언급 [언급]</dt><br>
<dd>mentioning; referring; reference</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 문제에 대해 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of talking about a certain matter or problem.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거명 [거ː명]</dt><br>
<dd>mentioning</dd><br>
<dd>이름을 입에 올려 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of speaking of someone by name.</dd><br>
</li>
